@using OpenCaptive.Application.Email.Models
@model PasswordResetTemplateModel
@{
    var hours = (int)Math.Round(Model.TokenLifetime.TotalHours);
}
Reset your password

Hi @Model.RecipientFirstName,

We received a request to reset the password for your OpenCaptive account. Choose a new password by opening the link below:

@Raw(Model.ResetUrl)

This link expires in @hours hours and can only be used once.

Didn't request this? If you didn't request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged until you create a new one.

--
You received this email because a password reset was requested for your OpenCaptive account.
Need help? @Raw(ViewBag.SupportUrl)
@Raw(ViewBag.WebsiteUrl)

